data.description:
*****SELLER WILL PAY UP TO $5000 TOWARDS SELLERS CLOSING COST & PREPAIDS*****
This adorable home was built by LA Homes. Very cute open floor plan. Concrete floors through-out home, Butcher Block counter tops & wood open shelves in Kitchen give it a warm touch. Features solid wood base boards and shelves in pantry & bedroom closets. You will love the convenient location of the laundry room in hall by all the bedrooms. This is also in the Loranger School or you can choose to send to Hammond Schools. Subdivision has a great play-ground just down the street from this home. You can join the neighborhood  Facebook group & get to know everyone, help plan events.
